<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. فَأَفْصَحَ القَبْرُ عنهُمْ حِيْنَ سَاءَلَهُمْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تِلْكَ الوُجُوهُ عَلَيْهَا الدُوْدُ يَقْتَتِلُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قَدْ طَالَمَا أَكَلُوا فِيهٍا وَمَا شَرِبُوا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَأَصْبَحُوا بَعْدَ طُوْلِ الأكْلِ قَدْ أُكِلُوْا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَطَالَمَا كَنَزُوا الأموال وادَّخَرُوا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَخَلَّفُوهَا عَلَى الأعْدْاءِ وَارْتَحَلُوْا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَطَالَمَا شَيَّدُوا دُوْراً لِتُحْصِنَهُمْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَفَارَقُوا الدُوْرَ والأهْلِيْنَ وانْتَقَلُوْا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَضْحَتْ مَسَاكِنُهُمْ وَحْشاً مُعَطَّلَةً<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَسَاكِنُوهَا إِلى الأجْدَاثِ قَدْ رَحَلُوا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>سَلِ الْخَلِيفَةَ إِذْ وَافَتْ مَنِيَّتُهُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أَيْنَ الجُنُوْدُ وَأَيْنَ الخَيْلُ وَالخَوَلُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>أَيْنَ الكُنُوزَ الَّتِي كَانَتْ مَفَاتِحُهَا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>تَنُوْءُ بِالعُصْبَةِ المُقْوِيْنَ لَوْ حَمَلُوْا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>أَيْنَ العَبِيْدُ الَّتِي أَرْصَدْتَهُمْ عُدَداً<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>أَيْنَ الحَدِيْدُ وَأَيْنَ البِيْضُ وَالأسَلُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>أَيْنَ الفَوَارِسُ وَالغِلْمَانُ مَا صَنَعُوا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>أَيْنَ الصَوَارِمُ وَالخِطِّيَةُ الذُبُلُ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>أَيْنَ الكُمَاةُ أَلم يَكْفُوا خَلِيْفَتَهُمْ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>لَمَّا رَأْوْهُ صَرِيْعاً وَهُوَ يَبْتَهِلُ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>